Machoke (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0066: Machop
Pokémon
#0068: Machamp →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Machoke (TCG Pocket).

Machoke has been featured on 21 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Machoke cards are normally Fighting-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Machoke

Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
